title: The Batman DVDrip Xvid Complete Series 2004-2008
description:
The Batman (2004-2008)

A young Bruce Wayne is in his third year of trying to establish himself as Batman, protector of Gotham City. Living in Gotham, a metropolis where shadows run long and deep, beneath elevated train tracks, this younger Batman will confront each of his familiar foes for the first time.

This is all five season in Xvid Format and the audio is MP3 from DVDrips. All ending credits have been cut out and all two part episodes have been combined together eliminating the "previously on."

All episodes should work on stand alone DIVX/Mpeg4 DVD players.

Excellent series. Please continue seeding as you can watch these on your computer while seeding. Thanks everyone for seeding.
